long_description: This simple and inexpensive airfoil makes your Yakima rack virtually noise-free! Airfoil shape smooths airflow over the middle of your bar, drastically reducing turbulence and eliminating wind noise. Snaps onto front crossbar, providing quick and easy installation. Only 8" wide, it easily fits between your accessories on the bar. Constructed with tough, UV-resistant PVC plastic.
short_description: This simple and inexpensive airfoil makes your Yakima rack virtually noise-free!
